{"tid":2422475,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德福廣場和你Shop非法集結案續審 張卓勤多次違規提問惹辯方批評","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:20:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4975a527e035136d15e10cce7881b29512c1240","tid":2422475,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"高級檢控官張卓勤<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2j5Wvi-axjdt-2m4HoWe08ZHWIc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QUNIVDOWMZEGHB4OODLWC2XWLM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2j5Wvi-axjdt-2m4HoWe08ZHWIc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQUNIVDOWMZEGHB4OODLWC2XWLM.JPG&h=2f33f328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前年12月網民連日號召到商場「和你Shop」，引發衝突，多人被捕。同月28日在九龍灣德福廣場被捕的10名青年，被控非法集結等罪，案件今於觀塘裁判法院續審。辯方多次反對控方在複問中向證人問及商場有否通知店舖關閉或叫人離開的廣播，直指相關問題在控方主問階段從未被提及。惟反對遭控方無視，而裁判官屈麗雯則著控方避免再問相關問題。<br />\n<br />\n德福廣場保安經理朱家培繼續作供。各辯方代表在庭上播放片段，向朱指出遊行人士當日在商場內只是「行」和「叫口號」，並無實質行動，當時店舖亦無落閘，商場內相安無事。直至警員進入商場介入後，才發生衝突和追逐，店舖亦相繼落閘，朱全部表示同意。<br />\n<br />\n控方複問時欲借片中背景的廣播聲，向朱澄清當時商場內有否廣播通知店舖關門或叫其他人士離開。惟辯方質疑有關廣播從未在主問或盤問時提及，故反對控方向無延伸性的問題提出覆問。<br />\n<br />\n控方未有理會反對，多次嘗試就廣播再向朱提問。辯方大律師郭憬憲斥謂：「反對，點解到而家Mr. Cheung（主控官張卓勤）都唔聽話？」庭內傳出笑聲，屈官即警告：「有咩好笑？法庭係莊嚴嘅地方。」屈官指示控方不要再問及廣播問題。<br />\n<br />\n控方及後再向朱澄清，當日有否收到店舖通知提早關門，朱表示「唔清楚」。控方提醒朱在主問時的回答是「冇收到通知」。朱重申：「我真係唔清楚個情況。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方嘗試釐清證人早前的說法時，惟控方反指「好詫異」為何辯方執著於供詞。辯方即謂：「請你收回批評。」控方拒絕稱：「我係唔會收回批評。」屈官則示意控方「有問題就直接問」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/55ODWCWHUFD5RLLEQ5JQO52SPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2F55ODWCWHUFD5RLLEQ5JQO52SPI%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=946fc7a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2F55ODWCWHUFD5RLLEQ5JQO52SPI%2F&h=37a5918e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/55ODWCWHUFD5RLLEQ5JQO52SPI/</a>"},{"pid":"b7484094c450402135153621435644122a77e86c","tid":2422475,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d30c6bd07f6e56dc903b763bfcc690a96aa389","tid":2422475,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e51af15e88ab7137f5558e5b9fca5126614920c","tid":2422475,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d30c6bd07f6e56dc903b763bfcc690a96aa389","tid":2422475,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4991bd80f71be0ffa220e2c3adbe09016bec445","tid":2422475,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"